{"tid":2324132,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有人無試過一路品酒一路屙屎","createTime":"2020-12-13T16:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T03:24:15.000Z","uid":9269,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"691bc1a55b7982dac2e1c79a68515cda63f919f4","tid":2324132,"uid":9269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T16:57:50.000Z","msg":"Well<br />\n啱啱飲飲下威士忌急屎<br />\n我2話不說就拎埋杯威入去屙屎同聽歌<br />\n係我屙屎果一刻<br />\n屎既臭氣同威係聞香杯既nosing同時衝出黎<br />\n但我覺得呢個係一個鍛鍊一個挑戰<br />\n係肛門爆出黎果下<br />\n成個人好想放鬆<br />\n但係為左避開聞到自己屎味又要聞到聞香杯傳出黎既nosing<br />\n個人要好集中<br />\n呢個行為幾有挑戰性<br />\n下次飲burgundy，我會試下一路屙屎一路飲"},{"pid":"5f7a8cf84596c950b23057a2ee9ad38da313a45e","tid":2324132,"uid":9269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T01:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e959926e80032ac0319e14168af0bf4c5e8f81a6","tid":2324132,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T01:53:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>試過一路品酒一路屌你老母</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae42325e5515740b6936a358d01ad2fde800d07","tid":2324132,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"read"}]}